div1.p:
Territory of Washington County of King ss.
To the Hon. C. H. Hanford, Chief Justice of Washington Territory and Judge of the Third Judicial District thereof, the undersigned Sheriff of King County, in said Territory, do hereby return that before me the concerning same of the annexed writ, the said William L. Tobias was committed to my custody, and is detained by virtue of and there writ, a copy of which is herby annexed; the original of which I also herewith produce hereintherof I have the body of the said William L. Tobias before you at the time and place in said writ mentioned, as I am therein commanded. J H McGraw Subscribed and sworn to before me the 18th day of Sept. 1889
